# --- Multi-turn scenario runs (reproducible LLM output) ---
# Each `scripts/run_scenario.py` invocation drops a JSON snapshot
# under tests/scenarios/<name>/runs/. These are throwaway evidence
# files: every run produces a new timestamped one and they would
# pollute git history. Findings worth keeping go into project memory
# or commit messages, not into the repo as data.
# Archive directories (runs_pre_v1/, runs_pre_v15/, runs_partial_*/)
# follow the same policy — historical evidence summarised in
# docs/v1_validation.md, raw snapshots stay local.
tests/scenarios/*/runs_*/
tests/scenarios/*/runs/

# --- Agent tooling / local state ---
.claude/
.claw/
.hermes/
.agents/

# --- Misc scratch ---
hello_tool.txt
*.log
rtk
aegis.tar.gz
